WITH time_range AS (
  SELECT
    $__timeFrom()::timestamp AS start_time,
    $__timeTo()::timestamp AS end_time
),
daily_data AS (
  SELECT
    date_trunc('day', time_stamp) AS day,
    AVG(price_eur) AS avg_price
  FROM "$Databases", time_range
  WHERE time_stamp BETWEEN start_time AND end_time
  GROUP BY date_trunc('day', time_stamp)
),
indexed_data AS (
  SELECT
    day,
    avg_price,
    ROW_NUMBER() OVER (ORDER BY day) AS row_num
  FROM daily_data
),
growth_calc AS (
  SELECT
    current.day,
    current.avg_price AS current_price,
    past.avg_price AS past_price,
    (current.avg_price - past.avg_price) / past.avg_price AS growth_rate
  FROM indexed_data current
  LEFT JOIN indexed_data past ON current.row_num = past.row_num + $custom_days
)
SELECT
  day AS time,
  growth_rate AS "Custom $custom_days DAYS - GROWTH RATE"
FROM growth_calc
WHERE past_price IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY day

)
SELECT
  day AS time,
  daily_growth_rate AS "1 - DAY GROWTH RATE"
FROM growth_calc
WHERE prev_day_price IS NOT NULL
ORDER BY day

order by x_i desc) as source

from
